  "texts": [
    "Images were not allowed to be the same in consecutive frames and had to have a female size greater than 0.3 and a female position between -0.1 and 0.5.",
    "• Optimize for lateral velocity: the same generation procedure as for 'Optimize for forward velocity' except that we optimized for the model output of lateral velocity.",
    "In this case, maximizing or minimizing lateral velocity is akin to asking the model to output the action of moving to the right or left.",
    "• Optimize for angular velocity: the same generation procedure as for 'Optimize for forward velocity' except that we optimized for the model output of angular velocity.",
    "In this case, maximizing or minimizing angular velocity is akin to asking the model to output the action of turning to the right or left."
  ],
